{"tid":1720750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"茶理史參與罷工 招牌被貼街招","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:29:37.000Z","uid":209657,"like":174,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"4baff24f6553396d630b22dcb90d3f2d66aa053e","tid":1720750,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2414432778824804&amp;id=1963709670563786&amp;sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2414432778824804%26id%3D1963709670563786%26sfnsn%3Dmo&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=b234b7ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2414432778824804&amp;id=1963709670563786&amp;sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n有人與於11月11日尖沙咀總店參與罷工期間，於尖沙咀總店鐵閘上貼出招租，幸得附近店主將其拍下及移除。<br />\n今早再次發現被貼上相同街招，這次更利用強膠貼於招牌左上方，而招牌為油漆塗面，￼￼￼<span style=\"color: red;\">暫時無法移除</span>。￼尖沙咀總店已參與罷工數天￼￼，確實被貼上的時間已經無法追究。<br />\n負責人今早已即時聯絡業主及街照上的地產代理，雙方均表示與其無關。￼<br />\n￼在此重申！尖沙咀店仍然存在！<br />\n#你咁做我係唔會驚㗎￼<br />\n#無聊無極限<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/75418224_2414413798826702_5297524374985768960_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_oc=AQkpY9ToxBLZCVMlp-nuWa9-_QKKC2EKoGiFC4NnJ67VIGXzXKEhQeXSG_BtRbLMOrE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=5c7b1f8b6b0d7e6eb265b472fc261afd&amp;oe=5E8763AE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F75418224_2414413798826702_5297524374985768960_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_oc%3DAQkpY9ToxBLZCVMlp-nuWa9-_QKKC2EKoGiFC4NnJ67VIGXzXKEhQeXSG_BtRbLMOrE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D5c7b1f8b6b0d7e6eb265b472fc261afd%26oe%3D5E8763AE&h=1a562971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記得幫襯下茶理史！！！"},{"pid":"1a3c01a75fb3ec0a52419f6eba9f7ec64a910f79","tid":1720750,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台